OL,3,CBusiness owner 'shocked' after HS2
OL,4,Cseizes site despite scrapping northern
OL,5,Cleg
OL,7,FHS2 has seized a site home to a
OL,8,Ffireworks storage facility, even
OL,9,Fthough the rail project won't pass
OL,10,Fthrough the land after the phase was
OL,11,Fscrapped six months ago, as ITV News
OL,12,FCentral's Pablo Taylor reports.
OL,14,FA business owner from says he was
OL,15,Fshocked that HS2 insisted on seizing
OL,16,Fhis site, despite the rail project no
OL,17,Flonger passing through the land after
OL,18,Fthe northern leg of the route was
OL,19,Fscrapped.
