OL,7,FSimon Boote is co-director of a
OL,8,Ffireworks storage facility in
OL,9,FSwynnerton - SGB World Services.
OL,11,FThe site manages and distributes
OL,12,Fseveral tonnes of commercial
OL,13,Ffireworks, used for huge displays
OL,14,Faround the world.
OL,16,FEarlier this month the site was taken
OL,17,Fover by HS2, which said it had been
OL,18,Finstructed by the Department for
OL,19,FTransport to take possession, despite
