OL,7,FSimon said: "It was shock initially
OL,8,Fbecause we'd had the announcement from
OL,9,Fthe Prime Minister to say that the
OL,10,Fline is no longer being built and
OL,11,Fourselves and the customers all
OL,12,Fthought that that was the end of the
OL,13,Fissue."
OL,15,F"Even on the day of the announcement
OL,16,FLord Stafford came down to the site
OL,17,Fhere and said to two of our customers
OL,18,F'oh we're all saved, it's all going to
OL,19,Fgo back to normal.'"
