OL,7,FHS2 had looked into the possibility of
OL,8,Frelocating SGB World Services.
OL,10,FHowever due to the dangerous nature of
OL,11,Fthe business, finding an suitable
OL,12,Falternative site proved difficult.
OL,14,FSimon Boote says he has concerns over
OL,15,Fthe expertise of the contractor HS2
OL,16,Fhas employed to run his former
OL,17,Ffacility, given how dangerous it is.
