OL,7,FHe said: "The main product that we
OL,8,Fstore here is professional products.
OL,9,FSo they don't have any instructions on
OL,10,Fthem. They're to be used by persons
OL,11,Fwith specialist knowledge so mainly
OL,12,Ffirework companies and people in the
OL,13,Ffireworks industry."
OL,15,F"Here now you've got a whole site of
OL,16,Fmajor hazard not under the control of
OL,17,Fregulations and under the control of
OL,18,Fexperienced people."
