OL,7,FIn a statement, HS2 Ltd insisted that
OL,8,Fthe staff now running the site have
OL,9,F'the correct qualifications,
OL,10,Fexperience and knowledge to run a
OL,11,Flicensed explosive storage facility.'
OL,13,FIt added that the government had
OL,14,Fpurchased the leasehold for the land
OL,15,F'before the cancellation of Phase 2 in
OL,16,FOctober 2023.'
