OL,7,FSince then, it had agreed that SGB
OL,8,FWorld Services would continue
OL,9,Foperating at the site as a 'tolerated
OL,10,Ftrespass' and that the terms of the
OL,11,Flease did not allow it to be
OL,12,Ftransferred back.
OL,14,FIt said the terms of the agreement
OL,15,Frequired SGB World Services to remove
OL,16,Ftheir fireworks storage bunkers from
OL,17,Fthe site, which the company had failed
OL,18,Fto do.
OL,20,FSGB World Services was compensated by
OL,21,FHS2 Ltd for having to vacate the site.
